longDescription:
Preview the collection on

”High Speed EDM - Volume 1" is a collection of 10 electronic tracks with an overall aggressive mood and fast paced rhythmic sections. The inspiration came from cyberpunk crazyness, modern and iconic synthesizers from the 90s, futuristic ambients and bold melodies, delivering all the energy you need in your projects.

The package includes multiple loops, intros and outros for all your editing needs.


Arcade Upbeat EDM Rock: Full length (03:32) 13 Loops, Intro/Outro

Brutal Electronics: Full length (01:53) 6 Loops, Intro/Outro

Dancing Stroboscope: Full length (01:11) 7 Loops, Intro/Outro

Deep Blue House: Full length (01:38) 6 Loops, Intro/Outro

EDM Green Technology: Full length (02:00) 7 Loops, Intro/Outro

Energetic Summer Party: Full length (03:04) 9 Loops, Intro/Outro

Save The Swing From EDM: Full length (02:18) 11 Loops, Intro/Outro

Slasher From The 80s: Full length (02:08) 15 Loops, Intro/Outro

Unstoppable Dance: Full length (02:11) 11 Loops, Intro/Outro

What A Night: Full length (01:47) 13 Loops, Intro/Outro

This pack is produced by Luca Tomassini a composer with more than 20 years of expertise in music production with multiple TV, feature films and multimedia placements.
